# BitOS Package Repository
# Format: name  version  description
bit-hello    1.0    BitOS SDK example / hello world script
bit-sysinfo  1.0    Detailed CPU, memory, disk and network info
bit-netinfo  1.0    Network diagnostics - interfaces, routes, connectivity tests
bit-monitor  1.0    Live system monitor with CPU/mem/process view (Ctrl+C to exit)
bit-diskinfo 1.0    Disk and filesystem usage with visual bar charts
